date: 2026-04-04
verification: verified-local
```

### Summary of v1.0.0 content

- Established core wave model: Phase 1 scan → Wave 1 (Haiku, parallel across repos) → Wave 1b (Sonnet, conflict resolution) → Wave 1c (Sonnet, CI fixes) → Wave 2 (Odysseus submodule pins) → Phase 6 verification
- Core rule: merge sequentially within repo (oldest-first), parallelize across repos
- Model tiers: Haiku for clean merges, Sonnet for conflicts/CI, Opus for orchestration
- Failed attempts from initial session: parallel within-repo merges, `--admin` bypass, Charybdis CI, Nestor rebase after merge, pre-existing CI failures on main
- Verified on: 5 repos (Agamemnon, Nestor, Keystone, Charybdis, Hephaestus), myrmidon swarm orchestration
